comment.body:
This is caused by `news.google.com/swg/js/v1/swg-basic.js` or it's inline counterpart
```
<script>
  (self.SWG_BASIC = self.SWG_BASIC || []).push( basicSubscriptions => {
    basicSubscriptions.init({
      type: "NewsArticle",
      isPartOfType: ["Product"],
      isPartOfProductId: "CAoiELOEKTb6Gt4di8rvnLo2HV4:openaccess",
      clientOptions: { theme: "light", lang: "ja" },
    });
  });
</script>
```

I wonder if this can be blocked as seemingly no actual use.
